         <div xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve" type="translation">
            <div n="r" type="textpart">
               <p>
                  <milestone n="1" unit="line"/> Zenon to Kleon, greetings. The water in the canal has not risen more than a cubit, so that the land cannot be irrigated from it. <milestone n="2" unit="line"/> Please, open the sluice gates so that the land can be irrigated. <milestone n="4" rend="break" unit="line"/> Farewell. [Year 30, Loios] 23, Mesore 23.
               </p>
            </div>
            <div n="v" type="textpart">
               <p>
                  <milestone n="5" unit="line"/> [Year 30, Mes]ore 24. To Kleon [...] water.
<note>Translation: B. Van Beek in P.Petr.Kleon, p. 59, © Peeters</note>
               </p>
            </div>
